        "To begin with, people who say, commercial campaign is extremely effectual to convince people to buy things think that it have the ability to force people to purchase  useful materials when they watched it. People mind is very curious, thereby if they influenced by anythings try to achieve it at any cost as a result commercial publicity can be a  necessary tool to convince people to buy the things which they watched. This has lead to increase the profit of business. For instance, a few days ago, I ordered a digital watched which I seen on a AD on Facebook. Although I have enough watch, I ordered it due to it infatuate me. Therefore, the more advertisement did a company, the higher chance their will be to get more order.",
