        "In conclusion, commercial publicity creates the path to business owner to extand their business and gets more profit. Some people think it is become auccessful at convincing us to purchase accessories whereas others think that it turned to common todays that people tend to ignore it. I think that deapite of some reasons advertisement loose it\u2019s popularity, it is still effective to persuade consumers to buy reliable products."
